column1: #text=I paid a visit to the library a couple of days ago .
#text=After getting off work at 5pm , I walked over to a library branch a couple of blocks from my home .
#text=I was looking to borrow a novel that I 'd been meaning to read for some time .
#text=I first logged onto one of the library computers to confirm that the book was still there .
#text=After confirming this , I went upstairs to the fiction section , located on the second floor of the library .
#text=Once I was in the fiction section .
#text=I walked over to the bookshelves and searched for the novel , successfully finding it fairly quickly .
#text=I then walk downstairs to the library 's checkout desk .
#text=I placed the book onto the counter and also took my library card from my wallet .
#text=I showed the librarian the card , where she then checked out the book after scanning my card .
#text=Next , once it came out , she handed me a receipt where the return date was printed on .
#text=Once I received this , I walked to my apartment with the novel in my hand .
#text=I was really looking forward to reading the novel .
